    <div class="panel" id="beautifully-light">
      <div class="photo"></div>

      <div class="container content">
        <h1>tech you'll want to wear</h1>
        <h2 class="h-sm">handmade in Sydney</h2>

        <div class="row">
          <div class="five columns">
            &nbsp;
            <%#= image_tag 'range/ive-side.png', style: 'width: 50%' %>
          </div>
          <div class="seven columns">
            <div>
              <h3>engineered light</h3>
              <p>Even with 39 electronic components hidden inside, every pair weighs just 26.5 grams and is comfortable to wear all day long.</p>
              <h3>balanced for comfort</h3>
              <p>By weighting the back of the glasses with electronics the frame is pivoted off your nose so it feels lighter and is less likely to leave red marks.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div id="visual-indulgence">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="six columns">
          <h1>visual indulgence</h1>
          <h2 class="h-sm">provided by Carl Zeiss Vision</h2>
          <p>By using Columbia Resin #39 for our lenses, we deliver 98% optical clarity without the weight of glass. Our sun lenses are all:</p>
          <br/>
          <ul>
            <li>100% UVA/UVB protection</li>
            <li>Polarised</li>
            <li>Anti-scratch</li>
            <li>Anti-reflective</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

      <!--hr id="model-divider"-->
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row" id="range">
        <div class="six columns" id="ive">
          <h1 class="frame-head">Ive</h1>

          <div class="frame-spec">
            <p class="spec">Single Vision Prescription or Non-Prescription</p>
            <p class="spec">Matte Black Finish</p>
            <p class="spec">49mm Lens</p>
          </div>

          <div class="model-detail top">
            <%= image_tag 'frames/ive/ive_black_optical_flat.png' %>
            <p class="bold">Optical</p>
            <p class="spec">Prescription Reading, Distance, or Non-Prescription lenses</p>
            <br/>
            <a href="/ive-optical"><button class="alternate tz-track"  data-category="the-range" data-event="buy-ive-optical">buy now &nbsp; &rarr;</button></a>
          </div>

          <div class="model-detail">
            <%= image_tag 'frames/ive/ive_black_sun_flat.png' %>
            <p class="bold">Sun</p>
            <p class="spec">Prescription Distance or Non-Prescription Lenses</p>
            <p class="spec">Polarised Brown Lens</p>
            <br/>
            <a href="/ive-sun"><button class="alternate tz-track"  data-category="the-range" data-event="buy-ive-sun">buy now &nbsp; &rarr;</button></a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="six columns" id="ford">
          <h1 class="frame-head">Ford</h1>

          <div class="frame-spec">
            <p class="spec">Single Vision Prescription or Non-Prescription</p>
            <p class="spec">Matte Black Finish</p>
            <p class="spec">49.5 or 51mm Lens</p>
          </div>

          <div class="model-detail top">
            <%= image_tag 'frames/ford/ford_black_optical_flat.png', style: 'position: relative; top: -6px;' %>
            <p class="bold">Optical</p>
            <p class="spec">Prescription Reading, Distance, or Non-Prescription lenses</p>
            <br/>
            <a href="/ford-optical"><button class="alternate tz-track"  data-category="the-range" data-event="buy-ford-optical">buy now &nbsp; &rarr;</button></a>
          </div>

          <div class="model-detail">
            <%= image_tag 'frames/ford/ford_black_sun_flat.png' %>
            <p class="bold">Sun</p>
            <p class="spec">Prescription Distance or Non-Prescription Lenses</p>
            <p class="spec">Polarised Brown Lens</p>
            <br/>
            <a href="/ford-sun"><button class="alternate tz-track"  data-category="the-range" data-event="buy-ford-sun">buy now &nbsp; &rarr;</button></a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="row" id="all-prescription">
        <p>All prescription lenses come with back anti-reflective coating, and a scratch resistant hard coat.</p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>

  <%= render partial: 'layouts/whats_included' %>
  <%= render partial: 'layouts/tech_specs' %>

  <div class="container"><hr/></div>
  <%= render partial: 'layouts/cta' %>
